@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bmaezg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp - ((v0 + 0.79 / v0 + 0.78) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.49)))
    v2 = v2
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.58 + v0 + 0.22) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.36)) + (0.68 * (v2 + 0.82 * v1 + 0.73)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.01)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
